# Place TLS certificates here:
# - ca.crt (Certificate Authority certificate)
# - server.crt (Server certificate)
# - server.key (Server private key)
# - edge.crt (Edge node certificate, optional - for edge node authentication)
# - edge.key (Edge node private key, optional)
#
# Note: This is ONE certificate for the edge node service, not per physical device.
# Physical devices can use username/password or their own certificates if needed.

